column2: HONG LEONG FINANCE NOMINEES PTE LTD

column1: PERCENTAGE OF SHAREHOLDING IN PUBLIC’S HANDS
AS AT 19 MARCH 2019, TO THE BEST OF OUR KNOWLEDGE, APPROXIMATELY 25.02% OF THE COMPANY’S ORDINARY SHARES LISTED ON THE
SGX WERE HELD IN THE HANDS OF THE PUBLIC. ACCORDINGLY, THE COMPANY HAS COMPLIED WITH RULE 723 OF THE SINGAPORE EXCHANGE
SECURITIES TRADING LIMITED’S LISTING MANUAL SECTION B: RULES OF CATALIST.
